Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.98,0:06:32.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}每次她與人結識,地都會震呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}美濃,什麽東西會震啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}太太,是地都會震呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.99,0:06:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}地震.....今早就有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.00,0:06:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}難道這不是預示了什麽嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.00,0:06:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我想時候終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.00,0:06:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你們好,我是  原千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.01,0:06:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這真是值得紀念的一天，我們深感榮幸
