Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.95,0:07:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}您是從.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}Rootasu電影公司來的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.95,0:07:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那是蓮花的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}噢,我很喜歡蓮花！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我知道，這就是我們公司名字的由來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}很快就是蓮花盛開的季節了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.97,0:07:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在詩歌裡,它們代表著.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.97,0:07:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是的！天真純潔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}對了,立花先生,您提過有東西.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.98,0:07:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}噢,是的！很抱歉.....
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.99,0:07:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我一直保存著這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.99,0:07:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}想在找到您的時候,把它交給您
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.00,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這麽久以來,我一直想遺忘它
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.94,0:08:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那鑰匙不是能開啟什麽很重要的東西嗎？
