Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可他留下的商店
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.96,0:09:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}讓我和母親過著富足的生活
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.97,0:09:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我在動湯不安中長大\n生活中充滿一次又一次的賭博
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.97,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}然而,一切最終都轉向好的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.99,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可我想,少女雜誌對我的影響最為重要
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我常常幻想著終有一天會遇見屬於我的王子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.00,0:10:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是不是就在那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.00,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}電影公司發掘了你？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.00,0:10:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我不知道.....
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}銀衛的常務董事從一個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.01,0:10:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}正在上學途中的扁鼻子\n小女孩身上看到什麽特質
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}實在沒有商量的餘地了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}一切免談
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.03,0:10:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.03,0:10:40.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}認為演員是一種前途堪憂的職業
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.03,0:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}前途堪憂？她是這麽認為的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.04,0:10:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}太太！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:51.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我們的新片將在滿洲拍攝\n它將大大鼓舞和激勵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.05,0:10:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}前線的戰士和國內的人民
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.05,0:10:56.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}毫無疑問
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.05,0:10:59.05,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子也願意為報效祖國出一分力吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.99,0:11:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}您也許是對的,可這孩子要去做演員的話\n還太小了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.99,0:11:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}她應該嫁個好人家\n把我們家的店好好經營下去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我說的沒錯吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.00,0:11:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}難道說一間糖果店比國家還重要嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.00,0:11:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}難道呆在家裡撫養兒女\n就不是女人報效祖國的方式嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.03,0:11:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}國民醫療周 祖國需要你！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.99,0:12:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.00,0:12:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我們到底在拍什麽啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.00,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.01,0:12:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我覺得自己像個偷拍狂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.01,0:12:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我趕時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}有點不對勁.....
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.03,0:12:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}要置身事外！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.04,0:12:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他不在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.04,0:12:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}往那邊！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.99,0:13:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}有沒見到一個男人經過？\n他拿著一個衣服包著的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.01,0:13:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他往那邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.01,0:13:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}快追！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.02,0:13:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.00,0:14:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}包庇這種人還真有勇氣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.01,0:14:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那是什麽人？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.01,0:14:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}能讓我看看嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.01,0:14:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這只是初稿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等我回到家就能畫完了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.02,0:15:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}到了冬天,眼前是一望無際的雪白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在那雪的天地中,我覺得逍遙自在
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:09.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我會畫完這幅畫,直到我冷得受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.97,0:15:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在那個純白的世界中
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.98,0:15:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你會覺得自己彷佛來到一個遙遠的異世界
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.99,0:15:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我好想去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}恩
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}為了報答你,等和平來臨的時候\n我會請你去的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.01,0:15:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}滿月.....
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}明天才是滿月
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可我更喜歡現在的月亮
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.01,0:15:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}滿月之後,月亮就開始虧缺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.02,0:16:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}再過14天又會盈滿,直到明天.....還有希望
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.96,0:16:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.96,0:16:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可你受傷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.97,0:16:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我的朋友在滿洲戰鬥著\n雖然畫筆算不上什麽武器
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.98,0:16:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這個？這是開啟最最重要的東西的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.98,0:16:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}最最重要的東西？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.99,0:16:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}猜猜是什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.99,0:16:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}不知道，不過,先別把答案告訴我,直到明天
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}說定了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.01,0:16:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}說啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.01,0:16:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你有喜歡的人啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.01,0:16:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}初戀哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.95,0:17:02.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我.....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}真是甜蜜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.96,0:17:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}老人也有過青春歲月啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那不就是你帶給她的鑰匙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.95,0:18:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他跑不了多遠！快去追！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.96,0:18:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}謝天謝地你安然無恙！有小偷潛入了倉庫！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.97,0:18:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他沒事,已經到了火車站
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.97,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你沒事,實在太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.97,0:18:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那個老店員！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.97,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這份工作好辛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.97,0:19:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.98,0:19:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.98,0:19:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等等我！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.99,0:19:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我一定會去的！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.99,0:19:59.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我一定會去找你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.00,0:20:07.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}真是戲劇化啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.01,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這一幕讓我哭了53次啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.01,0:20:20.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}喂喂,什麽時候變成了電影場景啊？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.02,0:20:27.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}從那個時候起,我開始拍電影
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.02,0:20:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.02,0:20:32.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那具體又是怎麽開始的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.03,0:20:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}還記得銀衛的常務董事說過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.03,0:20:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他們的新片會在滿洲拍攝嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.04,0:20:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}滿洲！沒錯！
