Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.99,0:29:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你騙我！
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.99,0:30:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我對你恨至入骨！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.99,0:30:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我對你愛至入髓！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.00,0:30:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}總有一天你會明白
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.03,0:30:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}老大！別！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.04,0:30:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}永  將軍,源右衛門願為您效勞！
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.04,0:30:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}咦？從什麽時候開始的？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.05,0:30:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}為了公主殿下\n哪怕上刀山下火海也再所不辭！
