Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.00,0:38:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我把一切都傳授給你,現在你卻讓我蒙羞！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.94,0:38:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你該學會聽話了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.94,0:38:08.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}傻瓜！惹火了泳子！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.95,0:38:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}活該！千代就是不知好歹
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.95,0:38:16.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}有幾個男人看上她,她就以為自己是藝妓
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.96,0:38:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}看牢了！別讓她再逃跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.97,0:38:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我們拍的不是紀錄片嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.97,0:38:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}說得太對啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.97,0:38:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}就叫七幽靈 -   原千代子的傳奇！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.98,0:38:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}瞧瞧現在老傢伙們！
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.99,0:38:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}小姐,你沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.99,0:38:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.00,0:38:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}交給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.93,0:39:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}從這裡走
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.94,0:39:07.93,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他就在城裡,對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.94,0:39:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你不會以為我會把你鎖在這裡吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.95,0:39:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.95,0:39:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}當你第一到這裡的時候\n我就覺得好像早就認識你了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.96,0:39:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我就知道總有一天我會幫助你
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.96,0:39:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}從那個時候開始.....
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.97,0:39:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.97,0:39:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}多少留意一下狀況,好不好？！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.98,0:39:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}劫獄？！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.98,0:39:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}有些反叛的武士逃走了！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.99,0:40:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}分散！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.01,0:40:15.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.01,0:40:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是我啊！你不記得了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.02,0:40:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我們相識在某個冬天的早晨,就像今天這樣！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.03,0:40:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我找啊找啊,不停地在找你！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.04,0:40:45.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}想把這個還給你.....
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.04,0:40:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}包圍這裡！別讓任何人逃了！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.04,0:40:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}等一等！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.04,0:40:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你的鑰匙！
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.05,0:40:59.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}保管好,直到我們再次相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.99,0:41:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那裡！快！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.00,0:41:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你看見一個武士從這裡經過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.00,0:41:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他往哪個方向跑了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.01,0:41:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.01,0:41:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我見過你.....
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.02,0:41:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你想隱瞞什麽
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.03,0:41:44.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}說！你知道他往哪個方向跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.03,0:41:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}哎呦！
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.04,0:41:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}別害怕,小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.04,0:41:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他終於出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.04,0:42:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}反政府的叛徒,受死吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.98,0:42:04.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你這蠢材！難道沒有看到時代已經改變了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.00,0:42:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}快走！小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.00,0:42:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這裡就交給.....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.99,0:43:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}小心！不要扭傷了！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.99,0:43:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}對一個賤民也如此關懷！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.99,0:43:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}小姐！我一定不會忘記的.....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.02,0:43:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在和我們玩做迷藏嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.02,0:43:54.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是去見某個人權分子嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.03,0:43:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我不明白.....
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.03,0:43:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我們有證據！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.03,0:44:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他在你家倉庫的牆上留下了點紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.97,0:44:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}真的？！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.97,0:44:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這麽說,你果然認識他
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.97,0:44:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那就夠了，剩下的，我們回局裡說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.98,0:44:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在那裡,你可得全招了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.00,0:44:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}又是一個硬骨頭！
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.01,0:44:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他們想知道什麽,你就告訴他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.01,0:44:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我不能說我不知道的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.02,0:44:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}就算我知道,我也不會告訴他們的
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.02,0:44:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我絕不會出賣他！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.96,0:45:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你這小傻瓜！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.96,0:45:08.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}現在你是這麽說.....
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.97,0:45:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可人是會變心的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.97,0:45:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我不會變心的！每一天,我只會越來越愛他！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.98,0:45:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}人就是這樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.98,0:45:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}聽說泳子把一輩子的積儲都給了她的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.99,0:45:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那個男人卻和另一個女人私奔了！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.99,0:45:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}怎麽她就遇不上我呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.00,0:45:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.01,0:45:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}又想幹什麽？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.01,0:45:55.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}小姐,我是來救你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.02,0:45:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.02,0:46:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你忘了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.02,0:46:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我是黃包車夫阿源,我來救你了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.96,0:46:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}為了報答你的好心
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.97,0:46:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我真的自由了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.97,0:46:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我不是說了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.98,0:46:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我們已經不需要你了\n我們已經抓到那個男人了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.00,0:46:47.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}不！等一等！
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.00,0:46:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}請等一等！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.01,0:47:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}開門！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.95,0:47:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}求求你！我只想見他一面！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.96,0:47:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}求求你！開門啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.96,0:47:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}求求你！快開門啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.97,0:47:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}接下來又會發生什麽事呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.00,0:47:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這是什麽？科幻片嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.00,0:48:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}蠢材！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.94,0:48:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}這就是你的報恩嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.95,0:48:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可是,倉庫著火了！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.95,0:48:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你這小傻瓜！你以為你可以就這樣去送死嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.96,0:48:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.96,0:48:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.96,0:48:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子！快回來！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.96,0:48:24.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.96,0:48:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子！快回來！
