Dialogue: 0,0:53:09.98,0:53:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你曾是銀衛的人？就在大瀧的劇組？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:15.99,0:53:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是的,可我只是個小小的劇組人員.....
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.99,0:53:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你不可能注意到我的
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.99,0:53:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你該告訴我嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.00,0:53:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃,現在你知道了吧.....
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.00,0:53:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我既不是導演,也不是場地總監
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.00,0:53:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}而且我總是惹大瀧先生生氣
Dialogue: 0,0:53:39.01,0:53:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我是立花源也,您好！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.02,0:53:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}好好幹
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.02,0:53:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}泳子,這是新來的源也
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.02,0:53:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我向來很喜歡您和\n  原千代子之間的對手戲！
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.03,0:54:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是啊,我總是襯托得她非常突出啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.97,0:54:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在她面前不要提千代子啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.97,0:54:08.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}記住這一點
Dialogue: 0,0:54:09.98,0:54:15.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}在這一行,我們要同時討好觀眾和女明星
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.98,0:54:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}下次我教教你該怎麽做
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.98,0:54:20.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}呃.....是的,先生
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.99,0:54:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}唉,那些話當然很中聽
Dialogue: 0,0:54:47.01,0:54:53.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子,電影導演就好比畫家
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.02,0:54:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}畫家將他喜歡的色彩繪在畫布上
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.02,0:55:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}而我,已經找到自己喜歡的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.96,0:55:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}那就是你
Dialogue: 0,0:55:15.97,0:55:17.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}用那種爛臺詞就想贏得她的芳心？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:18.98,0:55:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}下次我也該試試.....
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.00,0:55:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:55:50.01,0:55:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.96,0:56:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}對不起！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.97,0:56:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}日本麥當娜 -   原千代子
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.98,0:56:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我回來了！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:33.99,0:56:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我早就叫你全部拒絕的！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.99,0:56:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你知道,你不可能永遠\n都是人們心中的麥當娜
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.00,0:56:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}女人的幸福來自家庭！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.00,0:56:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可我.....
Dialogue: 0,0:56:49.00,0:56:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}打一開始就有這種罪惡的念頭
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.01,0:56:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他根本就沒來找過你！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:57.01,0:56:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}不！
Dialogue: 0,0:56:59.01,0:57:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我要去找他！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.01,0:57:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你連他是生還是死都不知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.95,0:57:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}他還活著！我知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.95,0:57:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你不會永遠年輕！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.95,0:57:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}我們約好了總有一天會再相見的！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.96,0:57:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}你已經是大人了\n怎麽還做這種小女孩的夢？！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.97,0:57:26.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}停！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.98,0:57:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子,怎麽啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.98,0:57:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}又要重來？我都累了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.98,0:57:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}老人家需要休息一下
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.99,0:57:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}第五次！
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.00,0:57:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}不見了！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:01.94,0:58:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}沒錯了！就是在那一天！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.95,0:58:10.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}泳子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:58:12.95,0:58:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}午飯時間到了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.95,0:58:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}還沒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:16.96,0:58:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}源也,到攝影棚去
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.96,0:58:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}公主可不高興了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:24.96,0:58:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}拜託！四處找一找！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:26.97,0:58:28.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}一定要找到！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.97,0:58:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}別呆站著啊！快去找！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.98,0:58:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.98,0:58:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}找什麽啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.98,0:58:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子的鑰匙！
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.99,0:58:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}原來是泳子拿走的.....
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.99,0:58:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}可那時沒人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:58:55.99,0:58:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}結果哪裡都找不到
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.00,0:59:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}鑰匙不會自己長腿跑掉的！\n一定是掉在什麽地方了！
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.94,0:59:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0008,,{\fn华文楷体\fs20\bord1\shad1\1c&HE0E0E0&\2c&H000000&}千代子,那到底是開什麽的鑰匙？
